  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses uterine fibroid research and education.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>requires the Department of Health and Human Services (department) to coordinate research and education related to uterine fibroids;<hr><ltbullet>permits the department to coordinate with medical research organizations to carry out the department's research and education coordination efforts, including data sharing;<hr><ltbullet>requires the department to report to the Health and Human Services Interim Committee; <hr><ltbullet>provides a repeal date for research and education efforts, and related reporting requirements; <hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes; and<hr><ltbullet>defines terms.",
